Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【第三銀河帝國歷 214年】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極限了…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究只是古代的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拖住本王40回合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是黃金的7人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷罪幻影！ 這就是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱然經過了200年 約定就是約定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然還有其他機體存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必道歉啦 晴人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 堂堂正正地就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 這可是寶貴的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我們學生會來接管它們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有這種資格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副會長 給它們貼上學生會備用品的貼紙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手 我絕不會讓你們碰Valvrave的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是經過投票被選舉出來的全校學生代表啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明討厭勝負之爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面卻依然是那麼固執呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當晴人露出那種表情時 是絕對不會聽從他人的意見的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一起離家出走的時候啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等下 別擅自就說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這話題挺可愛的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有翔子才會這麼覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長 最熟悉這些機器人的非晴人莫屬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把它們交給他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種獨斷專行的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我投翔子的意見一票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多數通過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是民主主義的決斷方式對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 要投票的話必須要由全校學生的參加…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 我還要調查這些傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查清楚後你們上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們老師可是有責任保護學生的安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人那個樣子的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是會有絕對的理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣CAIN上校的委託就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是在做戰鬥訓練呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是在解愁呢 Sanda那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟很想搭乘Valvrave的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為山田同學不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上去的話就不再是人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才沒有把找到Valvrave的事說出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然多虧了它能守護很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不好好抑制住的話就會變成野獸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副不死身就像別人的身體一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好我可能已經 死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人同學是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 愛娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼要聽指南翔子的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得會長說的很正確
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 通常的話確實如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里見 來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 那個…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高陽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 完全不一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥短路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3Q
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺會變身成青蛙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃對吧？ 加了好多好多蔬菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這芳醇的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你嚐嚐看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這個 能允許我委婉地拒絕掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流木野同學 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 喝些水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 只是燉菜而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡在喉嚨什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內涵勝過外貌的女人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在誇獎我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高級的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我做法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是意外的才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不意外啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你能來幫忙 流木野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼忙都幫不上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是又不想一直欠著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那次加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次很愉快呢 下次再來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這麼回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是很不錯的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EroELF！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是L-ELF！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點 這傢伙是多爾希亞的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是穿著校服…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指南翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下這個吧 這裡寫著這個國家的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
