Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生迪歐爾軍事發展與領土擴張相關計劃書？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員選拔測試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與ARUS締結軍事同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實行完全兵役制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把這個國家變成軍事國家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外沒有能讓這個國家存活下去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉決裂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有拉響警報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生迪歐爾的各位國民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家已經被我L-ELF-KARLSTANIN所佔領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來各位將成為全員兵役制的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為輔助國家成長的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄自己的生命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的政變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬冢久間 你那裡很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校內陷阱已經設置完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死的話就不要輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:09:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是咲森學園番長Sanda大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑吧 這裡可是三樓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠毅力啊！別小瞧了男人的氣魄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你在這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這裡沒有陷阱對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 我沒考慮到會出現這種狀況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要討回 之前的一箭之仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也只有現在能逞口舌之快了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流木野同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為連考慮的必要都沒有 如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子 還真是讓人想不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說流木野同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然突然就說要去幫翔子做料理了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那是回禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流木野同學其實很重視禮儀的 那個時候也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再拍一張嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也是那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊告白去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像野營一樣很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像林間夏令營呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃的東西已經有了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貼在膝蓋上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂得感謝他人的人一定是好人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(682,659)}              かみつき
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像跟晴人同學神靈附體的感覺一樣
Comment: 0,0:00:00.18,0:00:00.18,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(641,658)}かみつき                          かみつく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神靈附體？  是因為會咬人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 那個 我覺得晴人同學有著神靈附體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身 憑依他人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱著那麼厲害的機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得只有神才做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神靈附體… 神靈附體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的 比怪物這說法好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生迪歐爾的各位國民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家已經被我L-ELF-KARLSTANIN所佔領
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時縞晴人 立即來二年級B班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為國防軍的重點戰力 我要運用Valvrave
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太天真了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑一人居然以全校為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打飛腦袋的話 就算是你也會死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是15分鐘之前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錄音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼天真是保護不了你珍視的人們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍視的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 沒有紛爭的世界 那都是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-DREI！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只剩下一隻眼 我也不會看丟你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也預想到在這的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論如何也無法相信 你居然會背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信又能如何 你能原諒我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒這個打傷你眼睛的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會原諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是遲早要成為我的一隻手臂的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到最棒的一隻手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟掉一隻眼我也不可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒興趣充當任何人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了自己的輔佐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快解放學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不會成為你的軍隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把槍放下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放 學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒吧  L-ELF
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 都還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴生川老師 你是怎麼來到這的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是物理老師嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對會保護好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連計算都做不到的愚昧之輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-ELF 回來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從哪來的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q-VIER 打開艙門 捕獲他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是捕獲啊 Q-VIER！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔你還真天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去搭乘Carmilla打飛他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來藏在那種地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逃呢在逃呢 L-ELF在逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 Q-VIER！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒必須處死…這不是我們的教訓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的資質差太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺針？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去重練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:16:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被轟出來了 真是不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變更為B計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 採取包圍陣型 開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有部隊在外面待機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時縞晴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就特別地讓你們看看我的新舞步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了呢 H-NEUN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的 按照預定作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一單挑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我確實是想這麼做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以維持治安為目的而開發的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕獲用電磁吸附型迴旋鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來你的自由就被剝奪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流木野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時縞晴人到底出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流木野同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時縞晴人去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須切斷腳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這樣會影響Valvrave的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間移開這塊鋼樑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得出的結論就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫度在逐漸上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-ELF…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳被鋼樑貫穿了無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦 駕駛不了Valvrave的我已經沒用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的身體無法保證能啟動Valvrave
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我會相信你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是可能性最高的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4號機的放射熱已超過修養時的80%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死了的話你也會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種風險我早就計算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼抓回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有解決掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是幹掉了才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人 小心那些像迴旋鏢一樣的東西
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.82,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心電磁吸附型迴旋鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.82,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.82,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那個給貼上的話
