Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-NEUN 十點鐘方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這精準的射擊 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白刃戰嗎 正合我意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下 H-NEUN 跟他拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上了！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:28.37,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-NEUN對於接近過來的對手會傾向於選擇白刃戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-NEUN對於接近過來的對手會傾向於選擇白刃戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是預言家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.27,0:00:00.27,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:50.10,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標不是擊破那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:50.10,bar8,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是破壞射出裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標不是擊破那傢伙 而是破壞射出裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-NEUN 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是大意 對方是有L-ELF的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是背叛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們當今的作戰已經癱瘓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時撤退重整態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換到其他人身上去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被大家看到之前運到什麼地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 原來在那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是擋住他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你合作的話就能無敵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Licht…光？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
